PrecisDefray the charges and expenses of the public service of Canada within the Department of Regional Industrial Expansion or the Ministry of State for Science and Technology in relation to any matter to which the powers, duties and functions of the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology extend by virtue of the Department of Industry, Science and Technology Act shall be applied to all of the classifications of the Public Service within the Department of Industry, Science and Technology.
